<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />凡事都是开头最重要呀。<delay frames="40" />
就算是过新年，<delay20 />
也要注意别暴饮暴食哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />无论是大家一起享受庆典，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还是独自在家悠闲放松，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都各有过新年的滋味呢。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />新年刚刚开始，我就相当走运了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为能够像这样与你四目交汇，<delay20 />
恳切交谈<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你会去新年参拜吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />神明真的存在吗？<delay20 />
我偶尔也会思考一下这种事啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />与其说是去参拜神明，<delay20 />
不如说我是去直面自己的吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了重新审视自己的内心。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我听广播的时候，<delay20 />
占卜了一下今年的运势<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没想到我的竟然是大凶。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是这完全不成问题！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为我身边有你<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>